      "body": "Looking at the code around `retrieve_json` in [`github-merge.py`](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/contrib/devtools/github-merge.py), I don't see anything in there that handles pagination.\r\n\r\nThe code should be checking for `Link: <...> rel=\"next\"` response headers and sending followup requests if it's supposed to download all review comments. See https://developer.github.com/v3/guides/traversing-with-pagination/#basics-of-pagination",
